        Constructor of a hard token data.
        Parameters:
        tokensn - the tokensn
        username - the username owning the token
        createtime - time the token was created
        modifytime - time whem token was modified or a copy was made.
        tokentype - the hardtokenprofile used to create the token
        significantIssuerDN - of the CA that the card belongs to
        hardtoken - the actual hardtoken data
        copyof - tokenSN of original or null of this is an original
        copies - Collection of tokensn of tokens copied from this token, null if no copies have been made.
